Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8\fs21\be1}第十一回  「金崎的退路」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个不剩  都给我砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良大人  由我们来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半七  带着兄弟快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头领  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田家的猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有墨俣一夜城的话  我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田信奈和猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半七！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死都不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头领  快逃  趁现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能扔下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半七！半七！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…大…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你投靠织田真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把枪就赏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良  良晴先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你要平安回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出来多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾张兵还有一部分在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正情况简直乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  去救他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去只是找死而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是凭自己的意志留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护头领你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真柄姐妹立了大功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军的殿后部队完全崩溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的花只会在战场绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想让织田的公主们在余怀抱之中绽放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈已经撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有相良良晴率领的五百人左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田的猴子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长政对他的评价很不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军突入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良良晴的人头  一定是我们浅井家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光秀小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠猴子前辈  想活下来是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去救良晴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能光顾自己逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良良晴在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被浅井抢先了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌将的首级由我等来取！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六郎太！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的目标是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场上拿大将的人头才是目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要说是墨俣一夜城的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人头的价值肯定是很高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有那种价值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:07:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悬赏吗？不如我们来杀了相良也是一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮这个男人逃脱已经是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在这里  和伙伴们一起战死！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的尸体听到这话一定很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己舍命保护的男人  居然要选择屈死于此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田信奈  应该也是想说和你一样的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  她选择了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈是这个国家  大家都必需的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想让我怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说就是命的用法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了伙伴  你能去死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我绝对不会舍弃伙伴逃走的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是贪心  不拿到所有的东西是不会满足的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就死在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田家的猴子  滚出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始就四散而逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被老大吩咐保护你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果聚在一起的话  会全灭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别死啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人回来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里看到的  不要说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目标只有我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能放过其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的请求  是武士的情义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是你不配用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你了  假面大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些士兵就由我来给义景说情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你安心去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敌人拿走首级  是耻辱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  相良良晴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前  前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光秀小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良…前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是保住了性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算脱去了铠甲  还是把这个贴身留着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此挡住了子弹  削弱了威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子他…他死了都在保护公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人她…公主大人她抛弃了哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊  猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是梦呓而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直在呼唤着猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊  猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐快死了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守卫说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被狙击了  不知道能不能撑过明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去  有人吗  放我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明应该即死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田信奈难道有上天保佑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经跟死了没什么两样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人已经没用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  那家伙的任务已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过金崎的朝仓·浅井联合军三万五千人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始往京城进军了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田胜家率领的织田军  以一万五千兵力对阵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比叡山附近  坂本附近对峙着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破的话京城就会陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总大将·信奈不在的织田军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可以说是陷入绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴大人  粉身碎骨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么服部半藏要把良晴大人给…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把半藏叫来  问个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他已经保护着元康大人  返回三河了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田军可是大败了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个  现在问题在于公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她知道了相良良晴死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定没法活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说弹正大人对医术也颇有研究
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能救救公主大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心病是医术所无法治疗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的办法  只有强制疗法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让信奈大人自己去接受相良良晴的死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不会再醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝能誓下终生之爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子  你没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  婚礼的时候不要说梦话好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝愿认同相良良晴为夫  起誓终生不渝之爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事  怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意起誓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是梦的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  请进行誓约之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能从你这里拿到恩赏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我可是天下第一的美少女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你等到现在  真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信您会醒来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉脑子一片空白…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用了秘药  把梦和现实连接了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人  伤还没好  不能起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子他…死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炸弹粉身碎骨  听说连尸体都没留下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  公主大人  我没能救下良晴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  已经见不到他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明智光秀也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫也？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是高贵的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了他们  信奈大人也一定要完成天下统一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下统一…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨碍我们的敌人仍然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走了信奈大人的重要的人的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您打算就这样放过他们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能原谅他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  必须去复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子他们的  仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思  弹正大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈大人她需要活下去的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来代替相良良晴的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愤怒是最大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下一定会是信奈大人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬千代  赶紧去军师大人那一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田军把天王寺给烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是公主大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个堺可是有任何大名都不能进攻的规矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人到底怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是疯了  没有信奈的织田军只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织  织田信奈！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为猴子和十兵卫的复仇之战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们全部杀光！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会错  那就是织田信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主公  快迎击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没胜算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃回近江吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样就没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军前往比叡山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备守城吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  这都是为了把信奈变成余的人的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是朝仓军  近卫和津田他们也逃进了比叡山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让他们逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军完全包围了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气攻进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比叡山是有万人信仰的总本山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果进攻的话  就等于和民众为敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值一提…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您三思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是与民众为敌  我们至今到底是为了什么而战的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子都死了啊  十兵卫也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们甘心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀着怒气用兵  0分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不为了天下万民而战  人民是不会跟着我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了  公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是难以攻入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只要固守在这里  信奈包围网就能完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津田大人  其实啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就让津田大人去做和睦的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和睦？我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去拖延时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真有脸来见我啊  津田宗及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是作为求和的使者来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近卫大人给我了书状和礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  还来这套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重呢  到底送了什么来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗？织田信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你的猴子连尸首都没留下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你这个乡下大名不识相才会变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是个安慰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着这个头回国去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不悔改  还会白白牺牲很多人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和家臣  还有双亲兄弟的人头我会一个个砍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我什么都不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走  去追公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出阵  公主大人出阵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下如你所愿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了信奈大人好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军前进  但不可以随意进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相保持连携进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了吗…1分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:35.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ  時代の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:40.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}立たされて  戸惑う時に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:46.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を引いてくれた人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}出来ること探した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:55.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきながら  笑う姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:01.01,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の裏  涙が見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:06.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}救い求める声  聴き取れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:12.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}許された者だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:17.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}数え切れぬ  嵐を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:23.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの闇  裂くヒカリになる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:28.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう  迷わない  ともに生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:33.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓う夢が  どんな無謀であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:43.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おぼえていて  信じられる場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:47.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにあると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:35.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是深陷时代纷争的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:40.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无奈伫立  独自彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:46.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在寻觅着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生命中不可或缺的那个他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:55.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}坚韧的外表  寂寞的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:01.01,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}掩藏不住内心幽然泪下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:06.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛能聆听到救赎之音的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:12.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有寻觅着的他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:17.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}经历风花雪月的洗礼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:23.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}方知孤影的你似流光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:28.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不再犹豫  愿与你同存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:33.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算誓言之梦的前方是一片迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:43.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}请记住  属于你的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:47.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
